        ->  Sort  (cost=22.95..22.96 rows=5 width=10) (actual time=188.223..188.322 rows=2880 loops=1000)
              Sort Key: fa.actor_id
              Sort Method: quicksort  Memory: 25kB
              ->  Hash Join  (cost=18.29..22.89 rows=5 width=10) (actual time=126.544..159.900 rows=5462 loops=1000)
                    Hash Cond: (ac.actor_id = fa.actor_id)
